Dialogue: 10,0:00:00.44,0:00:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}So Kumagoro comes back in the morning \Nand knocks on the door of the old lady's house.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:04.73,0:00:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Knock-knock, knock-knock.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:07.74,0:00:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,"Who's this? Do you bring news of my father's death?"
Dialogue: 10,0:00:13.49,0:00:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}"You batty ole bird, yer dad \Npopped 'is clogs thirty years ago!"
Dialogue: 10,0:00:18.87,0:00:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,"It's me, Kumagoro the carpenter."
Dialogue: 10,0:00:21.83,0:00:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,"Oh, so it is. What are you after at this hour?"
Dialogue: 10,0:00:26.13,0:00:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}"I came to let ya know that, thanks t'you, \NI finally managed to make a delicacy."
Dialogue: 10,0:00:33.76,0:00:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,"Well now, isn't that wonderful?"
Dialogue: 10,0:00:36.77,0:00:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}"Learning to cook like that is a sign \Nthat you've really grown as a person."
Dialogue: 10,0:00:42.69,0:00:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}"You honestly deserve a great deal \Nof praise, young man."
Dialogue: 10,0:00:45.02,0:00:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,"So, what kind of delicacy did you make?"
Dialogue: 10,0:00:47.74,0:00:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}"Ah, well, I just handed o'er the package, \Nasked fer the guy's seal stamp,"
Dialogue: 10,0:00:51.41,0:00:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}"and let 'im know that if 'e didn't \Nhave his seal handy, 'e could sign fer it."
Dialogue: 10,0:00:54.78,0:00:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,"You dimwit."
Dialogue: 10,0:00:55.83,0:00:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,"That's not a {\i1}delicacy{\i0}, but a {\i1}delivery{\i0}!"
Dialogue: 10,0:01:01.04,0:01:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your continued appreciation.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:19.14,0:01:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I learned a lot on stage today.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:31.52,0:03:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to read manga, read manga.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:33.99,0:03:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Adapting it into an anime makes no sense!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.74,0:03:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd that come from?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.41,0:03:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you saying?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.28,0:03:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Why take a perfectly fine manga,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.87,0:03:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}where we do little more than talk in this room \Nday in, day out, and make an anime out of it?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.37,0:03:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, when you put it like that...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.79,0:03:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a point.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:52.63,0:03:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there you go. Gan said it.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.30,0:03:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:55.30,0:03:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop this!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.67,0:04:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}It may be unnecessary, but they're going through \Na lot of trouble to animate us in incredible detail!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.26,0:04:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a bit much to say the whole thing's a flop, Gan.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:04.22,0:04:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I said nothing of the sort!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:06.06,0:04:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You lot were on the verge of being convinced, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:09.23,0:04:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Dear God, if we're turned into an anime, \Nplease make it so Gan's the only one who doesn't move.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.19,0:04:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:13.11,0:04:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}At any rate, the audience is definitely \Na lot bigger than the manga's.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.24,0:04:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}But most viewers aren't watching this \Nthrough legitimate means.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.82,0:04:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Only lowlifes would watch a show \Nwithout paying for it.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.12,0:04:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Feeling like I'm being watched makes me nervous!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.62,0:04:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot. Just do what you usually do.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.58,0:04:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}The conversations in this anime \Nare written to be as inoffensive as possible
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.30,0:04:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}so as not to interfere with \Nyour enjoyment of viewing cute girls.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:45.47,0:04:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but "usual" is kind of hard to define, isn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.98,0:04:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What does everyone do usually?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.69,0:04:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ask such dull questions!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.40,0:04:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Shopping, I guess?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:53.94,0:04:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I read. Surf the net.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.03,0:04:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sleep.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.90,0:04:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that really a "usual" activity?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:58.95,0:05:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it kind of is, actually.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.74,0:05:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Sleep's important.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:02.32,0:05:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, in that case, I "usually" eat and drink.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.74,0:05:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, yep! Good one.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:06.58,0:05:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I usually breathe!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:07.75,0:05:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, yep! Good one.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:09.50,0:05:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I usually resent and begrudge.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:11.50,0:05:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, yep! Good—What the hell?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:13.71,0:05:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You need some more positivity in your life.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:15.84,0:05:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I live...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:16.80,0:05:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So the answer to "What do you do usually?" is... live?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.42,0:05:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the biggest cop-out I've ever heard.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.80,0:05:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So basically, I'd say eating, sleeping, and...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:27.77,0:05:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And rakugo! Right?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.69,0:05:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:34.44,0:05:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Y'know, as rakugo performers \Nwe should eat, sleep, and breathe rakug—
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.15,0:05:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey guys! What do you usually like to eat?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.32,0:05:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ask such dull questions!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:40.95,0:05:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}You mean if we talk about the usual stuff, \Nthings'll just play out like usual?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:44.03,0:05:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I would say the thing I eat the most is beef bowls.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:47.03,0:05:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, what place do you like best?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:49.00,0:05:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Knock it off. Don't go asking about specific names.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:51.91,0:05:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll cause us all kinds of headaches.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.13,0:05:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Yeah, but if we cut a deal to promote a brand, \Nthen we'll probably get to eat for free!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:57.59,0:06:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't think that'd be a headache?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:00.59,0:06:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to find it difficult to go into beef bowl places.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:04.05,0:06:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,How come?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.18,0:06:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,They're always packed with dudes.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.72,0:06:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}You can't look like you're trying too hard, \Nbut you can't look like you're not trying at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:10.02,0:06:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want to stand out or be an outcast.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:12.60,0:06:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Yeah, it's hard to pick out clothes \Nfor a situation like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.23,0:06:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, why make a special effort?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:18.11,0:06:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Just wear your usual clothes.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:19.94,0:06:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Sorry to change the subject, \Nbut we've been invited to a party.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.20,0:06:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,An invitation?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.49,0:06:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think you changed the subject.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:28.03,0:06:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:28.87,0:06:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Look here!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:30.87,0:06:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,"Please wear your usual clothes."
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.58,0:06:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Usual clothes.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:36.25,0:06:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Usual clothes.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:40.00,0:06:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,How usual are we talking?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:42.59,0:06:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,"Usual" is hard to define.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.55,0:06:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,"Please wear your usual clothes", pfft.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.59,0:06:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}That doesn't mean you can go \Nwearing your usual clothes!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:48.93,0:06:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}How many poor manga artists have been \Npublicly shamed by taking that phrase at face value?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:52.77,0:06:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Your "usual clothes" is just a tracksuit, isn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.98,0:06:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Wearing that to a party would be pretty uncouth.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.19,0:07:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Why have you all decided \Nmy usual clothes are a tracksuit?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.90,0:07:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}If everyone in the world went to \Na party wearing their usual clothes,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.20,0:07:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,it'd look like some sort of cosplay event.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.53,0:07:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Students usually wear a school uniform, \Nand people who have work clothes usually wear those.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:15.12,0:07:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Yeah, those are the clothes you end up \Nwearing the most, aren't they?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:18.46,0:07:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}So "Please wear your usual clothes" \Nis code for "cosplay party"?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:23.76,0:07:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's kinda saucy...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:25.47,0:07:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I definitely don't think that's it.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:26.80,0:07:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Who even knows that many people with interesting jobs?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.43,0:07:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I really don't think they mean work clothes.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:35.02,0:07:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}So they mean your civvies? \NI wear different things on any given day.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.77,0:07:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}You could just wear whatever you'd decided \Nto wear on that particular day.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.94,0:07:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.45,0:07:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Pyjamas count as "usual clothes"?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:56.54,0:07:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Well, they're what you wear most \Noutside of work clothes, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.54,0:08:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're right!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.04,0:08:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}I saw on TV it's fashionable \Nto go out wearing pyjamas in China.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:05.21,0:08:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.51,0:08:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}I guess it makes it look like \Nyou're a cool person who lives downtown.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:10.55,0:08:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Ah, but didn't they ban it \Nbefore the Olympics for being indecent?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:15.60,0:08:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I think we've found the ultimate "usual clothes"!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.64,0:08:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}In other words, "Please wear your usual clothes" \Nis code for "We're having a pyjama party!"
Dialogue: 10,0:08:24.94,0:08:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's kinda saucy...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.78,0:08:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I definitely don't think that's it.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.57,0:08:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Pyjamas? Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:31.78,0:08:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you sleep in pyjamas?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.87,0:08:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Wh-What else would I wear? \NWhen you sleep, you wear p-p-pyjamas!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.37,0:08:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what you said!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:39.50,0:08:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,When I sleep, I just let it all hang out.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:42.71,0:08:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Let it...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.04,0:08:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,all...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.25,0:08:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,hang...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.46,0:08:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,out...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.50,0:08:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That means Marii's usual clothes are... nothing!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:47.47,0:08:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not "clothes", you numbskull!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.05,0:08:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}So a "Please wear your usual clothes" party \Nis code for a completely nude party?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.64,0:08:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what you're saying?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.97,0:08:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's kinda saucy!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:56.64,0:08:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that goes a bit beyond saucy!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.73,0:09:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's strip her down.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:02.35,0:09:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Or should I say...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:03.11,0:09:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Put her in her usual clothes.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:04.94,0:09:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Gerroff me!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.32,0:09:06.36,Alt,,0,0,0,,Deal with it!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:06.36,0:09:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This is definitely not to boost the ratings!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.49,0:09:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's definitely not to increase sales either!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.28,0:09:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The hell is wrong with you people?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:14.07,0:09:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You're very sexy all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:16.37,0:09:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This could be the start of a new career direction.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.83,0:09:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It gets a lot sexier if you flip this up.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.87,0:09:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So it does.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:23.21,0:09:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though you can't really see any more.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:25.96,0:09:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out, guys!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:27.42,0:09:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,People are gonna start losing respect for me!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.67,0:09:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you really lose something you never had?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.84,0:09:34.47,Default,,0,0,56,,{\q2}Being naked all the time reminds me of a baseball manga... \Nthat I can't name because of copyright.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.47,0:09:34.51,Default,,0,0,-4,,{\q2}Being naked all the time reminds me of a baseball manga... \Nthat I can't name because of copyright.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.51,0:09:34.55,Default,,0,0,-67,,{\q2}Being naked all the time reminds me of a baseball manga... \Nthat I can't name because of copyright.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.55,0:09:34.60,Default,,0,0,-128,,{\q2}Being naked all the time reminds me of a baseball manga... \Nthat I can't name because of copyright.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.43,0:09:34.47,Default,,0,0,181,,What kinda reference was that?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.47,0:09:34.51,Default,,0,0,143,,What kinda reference was that?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.51,0:09:34.55,Default,,0,0,106,,What kinda reference was that?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.55,0:09:34.60,Default,,0,0,69,,What kinda reference was that?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.60,0:09:36.06,Default,,0,0,56,,What kinda reference was that?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:36.06,0:09:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way anybody's gonna get that!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.68,0:09:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's flippin' time!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:40.48,0:09:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like flipping the sheet will show more anyway!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.94,0:09:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:46.40,0:09:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This makes it look like I'm the nude one!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:48.65,0:09:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not having it!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.70,0:09:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it looks like I'm the nude one!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:55.32,0:09:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This won't do!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.37,0:09:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Make it someone else!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.45,0:10:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it looks like {\i1}I'm{\i0} the nude one!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.75,0:10:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Only fairies are allowed to be naked!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:08.67,0:10:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Now it looks like {\i1}I'm{\i0} not \Nwearing anything, glasses included!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:12.47,0:10:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.18,0:10:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:16.22,0:10:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Did we just...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:18.51,0:10:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfectly introduce all the main characters...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:20.77,0:10:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,For non-manga readers?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.06,0:10:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfectly?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.77,0:10:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone else!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.81,0:10:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What the? He's not even in this.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.28,0:10:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not a name!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.32,0:10:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not even writing!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.03,0:10:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Too long!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:34.32,0:10:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's "we"?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.57,0:10:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Not relevant!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:37.03,0:10:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to fix that!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.16,0:10:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be right back!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:09.73,0:11:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Greetings.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.96,0:11:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Greetings!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.30,0:11:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning, Kigu.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.63,0:11:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:37.80,0:11:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you listening to?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:39.30,0:11:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, have a listen!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:46.89,0:11:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:47.77,0:11:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Death metal!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.98,0:11:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Not what I was expecting.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:50.11,0:11:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Greetings to you!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.03,0:11:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What weren't you expecting?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:58.20,0:11:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Not what we were expecting...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.28,0:12:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, what isn't?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:00.45,0:12:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That you'd wear something like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.66,0:12:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure this isn't a bit of a stretch?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:05.29,0:12:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Rude! What do you mean by "stretch"?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:08.33,0:12:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Well, like when a fat person wears \Nunflattering colours like white or pink...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:15.34,0:12:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's called go-thick loli.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.72,0:12:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Go... thick?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.51,0:12:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, thick as in {\i1}thick{\i0}.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:19.93,0:12:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}There's also sweet loli, black loli, friend loli, \Ngranny loli, grampy loli, ugly loli...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.64,0:12:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}So what about you, \Nwhere you just wear whatever you like?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:27.27,0:12:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Erratic loli.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.23,0:12:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If you move your head like that, you'll...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.44,0:12:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Get-sick loli.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.31,0:12:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, we're...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.86,0:12:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Frolic jolly!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.78,0:12:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,They call permanent vaudeville theatres "fixed seats".
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.37,0:12:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,There are only four left now, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.49,0:12:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean there are still four left!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.95,0:12:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,They call the stage the "high seat".
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.58,0:12:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no "low seat" though.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.08,0:12:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}They say you "go up" to the high seat, \Nbut isn't it more like sitting {\i1}down{\i0}?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.88,0:12:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,When you start out, you're called a "Starter".
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.88,0:12:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,After a while, you get promoted to a "Second".
Dialogue: 10,0:12:56.63,0:13:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you get the right to wear a haori...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:00.01,0:13:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And the title of "Headliner".
Dialogue: 10,0:13:01.72,0:13:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew, it's a bit hot today.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.72,0:13:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, have some wind.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:06.68,0:13:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Wipe your face with this drama.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.52,0:13:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, guys.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.10,0:13:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}I get what you mean by "wind", \Nbut why did you call this a "drama"?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.69,0:13:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's what I use to drama-self off.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.69,0:13:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}I'm just dra-mazed you thought \Nthat was worth the setup.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:20.95,0:13:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at all these Dalai Drama!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:24.07,0:13:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,'Sup, guys.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.79,0:13:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Here comes drama.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:31.54,0:13:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the first thing you say to me?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:33.25,0:13:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, the tracksuit look actually really suits you.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:35.63,0:13:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, there's something quite... Marii-ish about it.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.84,0:13:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very you.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:40.17,0:13:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}I'm not sure whether or not \Nto take these as compliments!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:42.68,0:13:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.09,0:13:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, you're a rakugo performer.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:45.68,0:13:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You should say "greetings", not "'sup"!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:48.43,0:13:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I always get those mixed up. Either works, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:53.31,0:13:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You drama-teur.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.29,0:14:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The drum means it's starting.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.91,0:14:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}What kind of noodles \Ndo you want today, udon or soba?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.33,0:14:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ask such dull questions!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.13,0:14:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Soba.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.83,0:14:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Udon, I think.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:16.96,0:14:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Um?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.75,0:14:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we forgetting something?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:22.51,0:14:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Spices?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:23.22,0:14:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Chopsticks?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:23.80,0:14:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ordering?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.93,0:14:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah well.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:29.14,0:14:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Greetings to you!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:46.82,0:14:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,"Purr! Purr-purr!"
Dialogue: 10,0:14:49.95,0:14:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,"C'mon, I don't understand what you're tryin' to say!"
Dialogue: 10,0:14:53.46,0:14:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}"You're pawin' at my knees... \NYou must want something real bad."
Dialogue: 10,0:14:57.00,0:14:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,"What on earth could it be?"
Dialogue: 10,0:14:59.21,0:15:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,"Purrrr... purrr... "
Dialogue: 10,0:15:01.42,0:15:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,"Minimum service charge is twenty {\i1}purr{\i0}cent, sir."
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.76,0:15:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your continued appreciation!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.48,0:15:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, this is a tough question, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.28,0:15:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you guys dog people or cat people?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:22.82,0:15:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ask such dull questions!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:24.32,0:15:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}The conversations in this anime are \Nwritten to be as inoffensive as possible
Dialogue: 10,0:15:27.82,0:15:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}so as not to interfere with \Nyour enjoyment of viewing cute girls.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:32.62,0:15:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, this is so stupid.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.20,0:15:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:35.71,0:15:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I like them both.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.54,0:15:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:38.63,0:15:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And which do you like better, coffee or tea?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.59,0:15:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ask such dull questions!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:43.21,0:15:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Coffee.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:43.92,0:15:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Coffee for me, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.13,0:15:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If I had to pick, tea. The smell is so relaxing.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:49.14,0:15:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Tea actually has more caffeine than coffee.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:51.97,0:15:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:53.18,0:15:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Which do you like more, iced or hot?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.39,0:15:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Iced!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:56.27,0:15:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hot, I think.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.19,0:15:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,A cold bath or a hot bath?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.94,0:16:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Weird question.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.31,0:16:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hot, obviously.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:01.57,0:16:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hot, so they don't cheat you by using too much ice.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:05.57,0:16:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, you guys.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:06.82,0:16:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}A real choice would be something like \Ncrunchy versus smooth peanut bu—
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.24,0:16:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If I had to choose between cats and dogs...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:13.12,0:16:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What about sumo-style girls and—
Dialogue: 10,0:16:15.12,0:16:17.41,Alt,,0,0,0,,I like the sound dogs make more.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.41,0:16:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, even then it's gotta be cats.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.71,0:16:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dogs get to be in the zodiac and be police officers.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.00,0:16:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel sorry for cats getting left out.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.17,0:16:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Yeah, but then there are expressions \Nlike "dogs of war", which are unfair to dogs.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.01,0:16:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Cats have things like "what the cat dragged in", \N"cat burglar", "scaredy-cat", and so forth.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:33.89,0:16:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Evil spirits and stuff in folk tales are always cats.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:36.60,0:16:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You ever heard of a witch's dog?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:38.27,0:16:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They have that vengeful aura.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.73,0:16:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Dogs are too friendly to be ghosts. \NCan you imagine a dog with a grudge?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:44.15,0:16:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,They're just not cut out for it.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.57,0:16:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:46.53,0:16:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,There are loads of famous dog characters!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:48.57,0:16:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Cat ones, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:49.82,0:16:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Poop-flavoured curry or curry-flav—
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.82,0:16:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}When it comes to sound, \NI'll take cat over dog any day.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:54.08,0:16:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Sound?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:54.87,0:16:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, dog sounds so military.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:57.04,0:16:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Military?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.66,0:17:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Fetch!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:00.87,0:17:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you mean like military training?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.67,0:17:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, skill training.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:05.84,0:17:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,My dog has no skills at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:08.63,0:17:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want, I could bring him over for training.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:14.01,0:17:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:18.89,0:17:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I just hate the character for dog.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:21.10,0:17:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,How come?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.02,0:17:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes when I'm feeling uncertain and try to write it,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:26.28,0:17:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I forget where to put the little thingy.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:29.24,0:17:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.28,0:17:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:32.11,0:17:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Don't you find that the longer you stare at them, \Nthe less sure you are of which one is right?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:44.46,0:17:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Of course I don't!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:46.34,0:17:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:54.14,0:17:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You were hesitating for a sec there.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:56.22,0:18:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}The character for "dog" is a person \Nwith their dog beside them.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:00.64,0:18:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}They're carrying a hoe and \Nworking with their doggy by their side.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:04.52,0:18:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:05.44,0:18:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I just made it up!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.11,0:18:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Dogs just wanna be next to people.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.03,0:18:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me strength.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.32,0:18:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If that was the case, the thingy could go anywhere.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.91,0:18:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, or here, or here, or here, or even here.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:20.16,0:18:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Not there! It's being impaled!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:22.71,0:18:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it a bit lonely if there's only one doggy?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.17,0:18:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Poor thing!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.09,0:18:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Agh! Too many dogs!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.18,0:18:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,She's being attacked!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:37.89,0:18:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I've come up with a new character.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:40.43,0:18:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,"Grieving pet owner".
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.52,0:18:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just "big".
Dialogue: 10,0:18:43.39,0:18:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Um, this is a tough question, but do you guys \Nprefer the ocean or the mountains?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:47.81,0:18:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ask such dull questions!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:50.90,0:18:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a tradition.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:52.36,0:18:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Tradition.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.78,0:18:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.74,0:18:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so done with you lot.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:57.87,0:18:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I deffo prefer the ocean.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:59.24,0:19:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Mountains. More delicious.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:00.70,0:19:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Do you mean, "Which do you prefer, \Nthe sea in winter or the mountains in winter?"
Dialogue: 10,0:19:05.04,0:19:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No, let's go with summer.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:07.38,0:19:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Summer...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:08.67,0:19:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,In summer, decay is a problem in both places.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:11.59,0:19:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And exactly what are {\i1}you{\i0} talking about?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:13.59,0:19:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Where you'd rather die, \Nthe ocean or the mountains. Right?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:17.01,0:19:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,How the hell did you interpret the question that way?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:19.76,0:19:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Well, if we're talking about where to die, \NI think the mountains are best.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.64,0:19:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Get all encased in ice at the peak, \Nand get discovered hundreds of years later!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:27.85,0:19:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}The people of the future would be so incredibly moved \Nby my beautiful and inspiring appearance!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:34.44,0:19:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}How did we end up talking about \Nice-encased future corpses?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.70,0:19:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}The question is, which do you prefer, \Nthe mountains or the ocean?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:41.24,0:19:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Well, aside from which I like better, \Npeople are coarser at the ocean.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:45.16,0:19:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Coarser? Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:47.21,0:19:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,In the mountains, people shout:
Dialogue: 10,0:19:49.04,0:19:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,"Hello!"
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.46,0:19:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But at the ocean, people shout:
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.17,0:19:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,"You dumbass!"
Dialogue: 10,0:19:53.63,0:19:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:54.26,0:19:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.34,0:19:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}I really don't think people yell \N"you dumbass" at the ocean.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:59.55,0:20:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Oh, yeah? Then what {\i1}do{\i0} \Npeople yell at the ocean, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:03.39,0:20:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,"Catch me if you can!"
Dialogue: 10,0:20:05.39,0:20:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Though that's not at the ocean, per se.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:07.77,0:20:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It has nothing to do with the ocean, really.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:10.15,0:20:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That tanka poem about playing with a crab?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:11.61,0:20:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's kind of hard to shout a poem.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:14.36,0:20:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.36,0:20:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If you fell in a hole on the beach—
Dialogue: 10,0:20:16.65,0:20:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:21.12,0:20:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it {\i1}is{\i0} "you dumbass".
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.62,0:20:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, "you dumbass".
Dialogue: 10,0:20:24.08,0:20:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,"You dumbass".
Dialogue: 10,0:20:26.12,0:20:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Right? Right? Right?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:27.25,0:20:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose she's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:28.67,0:20:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't come up with anything else.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:30.13,0:20:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Doesn't it change depending on \Nwhich ocean you're shouting it at?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.75,0:20:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,How d'you mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:36.34,0:20:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}I think you'd shout different things depending on \Nwhether you're facing the Sea of Japan or the Pacific Ocean.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:41.22,0:20:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,On the Pacific side, there's nobody to shout to.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:44.81,0:20:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}To shout at King Kamehameha, your voice has to \Ncarry six thousand four hundred kilometres.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:48.56,0:20:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Too far!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:49.48,0:20:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}"You dumbass" travels at \Nthree hundred forty meters per second.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:53.40,0:20:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,How long does it take to arrive?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:57.24,0:21:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it quicker to shorten it to "dumbass"?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.03,0:21:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it definitely gets your point across faster.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:04.37,0:21:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}The Sea of Japan has stuff \Nthat's a lot nearer, so you should shout...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:13.88,0:21:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew she wouldn't think of anything.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:15.63,0:21:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,"You dumbass" works perfectly fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:17.63,0:21:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Just don't read too much into it.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:20.01,0:21:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}"You dumbass" can cover a fairly wide angle. \NBut don't read too much into it.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:25.18,0:21:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}The issue with "you dumbass" is that it's so rude, \Nit probably won't resolve anything.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:30.98,0:21:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Resolve?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:32.06,0:21:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got it.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:37.03,0:21:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.65,0:21:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that should do the trick!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:40.82,0:21:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You should shout "Give it back!" at the ocean.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:43.91,0:21:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:44.66,0:21:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:45.45,0:21:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It basically covers every angle.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:50.00,0:21:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Give back the Northern Territories!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:54.46,0:21:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Give back our citizens!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:58.71,0:22:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Give back our technology!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:02.76,0:22:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Give back our submarine resources!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:06.76,0:22:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Give back everyone's money!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:40.94,0:23:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Tetora Bouhatei here.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:42.86,0:23:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for stopping by.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:47.20,0:23:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure has been hot and humid lately, eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:49.78,0:23:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Be careful. If you sleep with the AC on, \Nyou'll get ill, so make sure you avoid that.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:57.25,0:23:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}So anyway, here's what's \Nin the next episode of Rakugo Girls:
Dialogue: 10,0:24:00.17,0:24:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}"Backstage Wealth", "Tower Trip", \Nand "Girl with a Cold".
Dialogue: 10,0:24:06.55,0:24:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,See you there!
